name: red-black-data
short_description: Red-Black Maps and Trees, written in Java. These Classes try to advoid the overhead produced by Sun's implementations. For example Trees are just Trees, nor self mapped Maps. Access on nodelevel is possible, reducing overhead while iterating over an map
